      "metadata": {
        "title": "LOVOO - Dating App & Chat App",
        "subtitle": "to flirt or find new friends",
        "promotional_text": null,
        "description": "LOVOO will\u2026   \n- spark your curiosity.  \n- cherish what makes you unique.   \n- prioritize your needs.   \n- let you get to know people in a variety of ways.  \n- help you find friends.\n- introduce you to genuine singles near you.    \n- simplify planning your date.   \n- focus on your safety when dating. \n- let you discover all the facets of love. \n- be a loyal companion on your adventures.   \n\nIt\u2019s not pronounced \u201clohfou\u201d or \u201cloowoo\u201d, but \u201cluh-voo\u201d \u2013 sounds almost like \"love you\", doesn't it?\n\nEach month, there are millions of millions of matches, chats and dates  on LOVOO! Be open. Take the first step. \n\n// How to get started: \nMore than just photos: Showcase your personality in your dating profile. Charming, honest and humorous profile questions make chatting and flirting easier. \n\n// Personal recommendations \u2013 Best Picks: \nMatches with value: With Best Picks, we introduce you to new people each day with whom you have something in common.  \n\n// Dating from your couch \u2013 in our live video chat: \nGet to know each other in the privacy of a video chat and see if you're compatible. \n \n// We're reinventing Radar \u2013 the map to help you plan your dates: \nDiscover singles in your area, find great places for a first date, share meeting places with matches, and claim special offers.   \n \n// Start a conversation: Matches, chats & icebreakers \nInstant chemistry with someone you discovered on Match? Write to new people instantly and flirt easily without a match using the Icebreaker feature. \n\n// Flirts at a glance: \nBrowse the flirt gallery and see who likes you or visited your profile. \n\n// Go on a live video date today:\nMore than just your classic dating app: Start a speed date with \u2018next|date\u2019 and decide if it\u2019s a match and if you\u2019d like to schedule the next date. Before you interact in a chat or in Match, a blind date lets you score points for your personality, humor and voice. \n\n// Better than TV \u2013 LOVOO Live: \nMeet different personalities in live streams and live chats. Give entertaining streamers virtual gifts or start your own show. Friends and couples have also found each other here. \n \n// A safe place for lighthearted flirting: \nFakes and scams have no place on LOVOO. Policies and procedures are in place to ensure your safety when meeting new people. You can report inappropriate behavior, suspicious profiles, etc. at any time.\n\nMore information is available in the Terms of Use (https://www.lovoo.com/en/termsandconditions/) and Privacy Policy (https://www.lovoo.com/en/privacypolicy/).",
